https://twitter.com/_zeets/status/1506728441420431361</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/l9wYYCf</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ednl]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Story time with Mr. Lawson</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/zlkNyLl</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/H6deGhJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is a tried and true social experiment that students learn the value of common resource.

Sorry, for the bad title.  Students take from a bowl of gold fish to simulate fishing from a pond.  The population of goldfish are repopulated at the end of the round (1 fish per every 3 remaining).</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qjMkQqH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I set up the experiment with some ground rules that were outside the norm.  You could buy houses that had refrigeration. They could buy cars that allowed them to go between tables if you wanted to trade fish or commodities. And fishing poles if you wanted to increase your time to harvest (from 3sec to 5sec)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gqHwyll.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I had one final rule, if you wanted to be creative and expand the rules you could if you had real world examples. Example, "can we sell fish we kept for later use if we have a fridge from the house we bought?". Yes!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mlImSmD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Honestly, it happened so fast I just had to sit back and watch.  Students were rejecting refugees from other tables who miss managed their resources. Others were extorting the poor by hording the fish in refrigeration and selling them for 100x the market value. One kid jokingly offered a fellow student for fish or cash.  A stratification of social standings was created of the haves and the have nots.  Soon war broke out over the resources.  The numbers were strong with the poor masses but like the game risk I gave more dice to the table that could afford more military equipment.  It culminated in a world war that had no winner.  All the resources were harvested and sold to pay for each sides war machines.  These resources then became unsustainable and all parties starved to death to end the experiment.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h3FAY9P.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The reflection papers that came out of that one experiment were the best I've ever read.  Students who never write; wrote multi page essays on the interworking of society and the pitfalls of human nature when faced with situations like starvation, war, and discrimination.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/zlkNyLl</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Letsleepnotphaseme]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>NY needs to indict Trump. Prosecutor resignation letter just leaked by NYT.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/seTvvWO</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Y6KQuyC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SkQUm4R.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Below is the full text of Prosecutor Mark Pomerantz’s resignation letter.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RYwIPeY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FNalT5x.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SSKx4QG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/J8hRc5v.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IbKOzd7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EVKJAaq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h7kFmEK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/98dPrbq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/